WEBVTT

00:00:02.940 --> 00:00:06.735 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bible is the world’s most popular book.

00:00:08.028 --> 00:00:10.906 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You may already have a copy in your home.

00:00:11.740 --> 00:00:14.243 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Its wisdom can help you and your family

00:00:14.243 --> 00:00:16.453 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to enjoy life now

00:00:16.453 --> 00:00:18.497 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and gain a real hope for the future.

00:00:20.416 --> 00:00:23.794 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s Witnesses
offer a home Bible study program

00:00:23.794 --> 00:00:27.047 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that is designed to help you
get the most out of your own Bible.

00:00:28.966 --> 00:00:31.844 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You will not be taught religious traditions

00:00:31.844 --> 00:00:34.471 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—only what the Bible teaches.

00:00:36.599 --> 00:00:38.642 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bible study is free,

00:00:38.642 --> 00:00:40.728 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and there is no charge for the Bible

00:00:40.728 --> 00:00:43.063 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or Bible study publication you will use.

00:00:46.901 --> 00:00:49.403 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You choose when, where,

00:00:49.403 --> 00:00:51.530 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and how often you would like to study.

00:00:52.531 --> 00:00:55.576 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You will consider Bible subjects by topic.

00:00:56.702 --> 00:00:59.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A study session
may be as short as ten minutes

00:00:59.204 --> 00:01:01.624 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or up to an hour or more.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.211 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Regardless of where
or when you choose to study,

00:01:06.211 --> 00:01:09.048 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you are not obligated
to become one of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:01:10.925 --> 00:01:13.761 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There are no tests or exams.

00:01:13.761 --> 00:01:16.055 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And you can learn at your own pace.

00:01:17.848 --> 00:01:20.476 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The lessons include illustrations and videos

00:01:20.476 --> 00:01:24.313 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that make learning easier and more enjoyable.

00:01:24.313 --> 00:01:26.857 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You’ll have the opportunity to read

00:01:26.857 --> 00:01:30.736 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and research the material before you
discuss it with one of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:01:31.862 --> 00:01:34.740 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Study sessions
can be held at your home,

00:01:35.783 --> 00:01:37.826 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
over the phone,

00:01:39.536 --> 00:01:41.747 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or via videoconferencing.

00:01:44.541 --> 00:01:47.378 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You’ll learn how to apply the Bible’s wisdom

00:01:47.378 --> 00:01:50.172 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so that you can enjoy life to the full.

00:01:53.175 --> 00:01:55.386 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To request a Bible study,

00:01:55.386 --> 00:01:58.263 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
speak to one of Jehovah’s Witnesses

00:01:58.263 --> 00:02:00.933 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or go to jw.org.

